sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as Chat Client
  participant GW as Gateway
  participant CS as chat-service
  participant US as user-service
  participant FS as forum-service
  participant DB as chat DB

  UI->>GW: GET /api/chat/groups/:groupId/messages
  GW->>CS: request
  CS->>US: verify auth token
  US-->>CS: userId
  CS->>FS: check membership(groupId,userId)
  alt user is member
    FS-->>CS: allowed
    CS->>DB: query recent Message rows
    CS-->>UI: 200 messages
  else user not member
    FS-->>CS: denied
    CS-->>UI: 403 forbidden
  end
